Management
The Orange Harbor Board of Directors sets policy, but it is implemented by the on-site office and maintenance staff.  Friendly. Helpful. Courteous. Your feedback is always encouraged.
Contact Information
Management Office: 239-694-3707
Home Sales Office: 877-360-7577
RV Information: 239-694-3707
Office Hours
Management Office:
Monday - Friday; 10 a.m to 4 p.m.
If no answer, be sure to leave a message! Newby Management is the management company. For after-hours emergency, call 844-285-2099 (residents only).
​
Home Sales Office:
Monday - Friday; 10 a.m. to 2 p.m.
Weekends and after hours: agents available by appointment
For immediate assistance by a Realtor, call 877-360-7577.
​
